Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.21,0:01:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,They seem strange and alien.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.85,0:01:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Primitive and peculiar,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.97,0:01:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,they are unlike any flora or fauna known to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.93,0:01:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Since time immemorial,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.77,0:01:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,men have feared these misshapen entities,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.25,0:02:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,which came to be known as "mushi."
