Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.91,0:02:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.83,0:02:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What is this scent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.47,0:02:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It smells like a rich fruit wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.79,0:02:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Is it kouki?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.25,0:02:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In a place like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.51,0:02:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No, it can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.03,0:02:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The scent suddenly turned a little sour.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:57.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's coming from that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.41,0:02:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's something there.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.43,0:03:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.07,0:03:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}looking at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.35,0:03:11.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}My body's petrified.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.47,0:03:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.03,0:03:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Now just stay put.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.77,0:03:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A person?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.31,0:03:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn. It's just a person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.83,0:03:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.06,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess you can go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.15,0:03:38.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can finally breathe again.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.55,0:03:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Who was that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}A hunter?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Couldn't be. I didn't see any weapons on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.19,0:03:48.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not to mention...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.29,0:03:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}that sweet scent disappeared with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.15,0:03:53.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Just what...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.93,0:03:55.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}was that all about?
