Dialogue: 2,0:03:58.59,0:04:04.55,Mushisode Title,,0,0,0,eptitle,{\an6\fad(2000,0)\blur0.6\pos(1210,110)}The Hand that Caresses the Night
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.09,0:04:11.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Man, last night was pretty tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.87,0:04:17.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll eat something to get my energy back up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.71,0:04:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't have any dried meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.91,0:04:32.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Nah, {we }haven't had much luck hunting lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.59,0:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.61,0:04:36.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:39.51,Default,,0,0,0,,That boy seems to be selling some.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.51,0:04:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, him. I'd advise against it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.73,0:04:46.08,Default,,0,0,0,,His meat always reeks.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}He's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.20,0:04:55.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The meat does smell a bit rotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.99,0:04:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Have any fresh meat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.27,0:04:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,There's some at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.87,0:05:02.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Can I tag along and buy some of that instead?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.37,0:05:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.51,0:05:06.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Follow me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.83,0:05:19.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.34,0:05:24.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The meat inside the house smells rotten too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.87,0:05:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,There's someone who'd like to buy some of this morning's catch.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.55,0:05:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.31,0:05:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.83,0:05:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Who is it, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.30,0:05:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,This doesn't happen often.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.25,0:05:41.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}There's a sweet smell in the midst of the rotten one.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.87,0:05:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is the same scent from last night in the mountains.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.41,0:05:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey. A traveler, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.77,0:05:55.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.37,0:05:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You can pick out whatever you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.29,0:06:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you hunting in the mountains last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.69,0:06:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just butchered these this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.21,0:06:11.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've been letting them sit out in the sun all day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.01,0:06:13.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.23,0:06:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you saying our meat stinks?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.93,0:06:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,In what way?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.18,0:06:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I{\i0} don't smell anything wrong with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.44,0:06:20.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Usuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.15,0:06:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.56,0:06:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go catch you something fresh.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.79,0:06:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't have any complaints then, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.29,0:06:29.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry. I'll only be a half hour or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.73,0:06:32.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Just sit tight for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.91,0:06:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.03,0:06:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.09,0:07:01.12,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.63,0:07:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.47,0:07:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.09,0:07:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.79,0:07:20.68,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.39,0:07:25.46,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no wonder all your meat tastes bad regardless of how fresh it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.27,0:07:31.39,Default,,0,0,0,,That hand of yours that helps you hunt...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.13,0:07:34.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Any relatives of yours have the same ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.81,0:07:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.09,0:07:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Our father had it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:43.48,Default,,0,0,0,,And on the palm, there's a mark shaped like an eye, correct?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.91,0:07:48.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That mark is proof that you're tainted by fuki, the "Sake of Decay."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:08:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki is a decayed form of kouki, which is the essence of all life.{Kouki is also called the "Sake of Light" earlier on in the series.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.39,0:08:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Unable to become the \Nmushi it was meant to be,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.08,0:08:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it can be found in groundwater and resembles reddish mud.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.49,0:08:12.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It smells much like fruit wine, but it is toxic.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.19,0:08:16.12,Default,,0,0,0,,If ingested in high enough concentrations, it usually causes death.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.41,0:08:21.44,Default,,0,0,0,,However, a small number of people are able to tolerate it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.01,0:08:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Fuki itself is not sentient.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.63,0:08:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It is merely a "thing" of decay.{it just sits there, "waiting" for more decay}{i guess the original line can stay if it sounds better}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.83,0:08:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But once it is ingested and enters the bloodstream,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.17,0:08:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,the fuki {\i1}becomes{\i0} sentient,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.58,0:08:37.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and its host gains a special ability:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.59,0:08:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the ability to give off a sweet smell from their hand,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.39,0:08:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,which lures in and intoxicates prey.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.31,0:08:51.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The fuki is then passed down through that host's bloodline for generations.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.23,0:08:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so {\i1}that's{\i0} what this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.85,0:09:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,However, only a few can actually gain the ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.19,0:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The descendants who cannot... \Noften do not survive the fuki's toxicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.87,0:09:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Granny died coughing up blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.75,0:09:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,My little brother has the same illness she did.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You're saying that's also because of this fuki thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.47,0:09:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,There's got to be some way to cure it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.99,0:09:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,If we don't do something, Usuke could{ end up like her}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.65,0:09:21.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Not to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.07,0:09:22.33,Default,,0,0,0,,There is a cure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.09,0:09:26.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If the afflicted person drinks enough kouki, \Nthe fuki will dissipate.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.79,0:09:29.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have enough with me right now, \Nbut I can get you some.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.64,0:09:31.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.53,0:09:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's great news, isn't it, Usuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.22,0:09:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,You won't have to put up with that illness much longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.29,0:09:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.75,0:09:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Your brother isn't the only one who needs treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.73,0:09:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.78,0:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm fine, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.55,0:09:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad... How'd he die?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.53,0:09:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Since you know, that makes this easier.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.67,0:09:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,We should cure yours as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.52,0:10:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You're healthy and strong enough as you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.08,0:10:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you'll have no problem hunting, even without that ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.09,0:10:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll bring back enough for both of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.25,0:10:14.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I shouldn't be longer than a month or so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.17,0:10:16.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks for your help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.61,0:10:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Until I get back, try not to hunt another human by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.65,0:10:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait... that was {\i1}you{\i0} in the mountains last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.83,0:10:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you always hunt at night?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.48,0:10:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.05,0:10:36.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Many wild animals are more active at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.34,0:10:41.33,Default,,0,0,0,,The only ones around during the day are birds that can't see too well at night.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.33,0:10:44.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Small birds aren't much of a challenge, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.05,0:10:46.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You should at least carry a lantern, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.46,0:10:48.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's misleading and reckless not to.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.27,0:10:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,But if I do, no wild beast will come near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.20,0:10:55.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, I could get around these mountains blindfolded,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and no animal is brave enough to attack me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.79,0:11:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The moonlight's more than enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.79,0:11:06.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you see yourself as the king of the mountain or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.55,0:11:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You're just a part of these mountains too, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.21,0:11:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Nobody can predict what will or won't kill them,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.93,0:11:21.24,Default,,0,0,0,,not even the most feared mountain beasts.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.67,0:11:24.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.58,0:11:26.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll try to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.99,0:11:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.60,0:11:36.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Take the medicine, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.51,0:11:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I want the old Tatsu back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.69,0:11:43.14,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.13,0:11:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like I've changed any, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:33.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.94,0:12:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you find enough medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, I have it with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.43,0:12:38.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Out hunting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.15,0:12:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Same as before, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.88,0:12:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,And at such a late hour...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.21,0:12:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Ginko!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.26,0:12:46.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.95,0:12:48.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.60,0:12:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Please give Tatsu his medicine right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:09.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Did... Tatsu do all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.79,0:13:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Ever since Dad died, Tatsu started to become more like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad would do this a lot too... He was always killing animals we didn't need.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Here. Take that home{,} and butcher it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.91,0:13:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Dad, we've still got plenty at home.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Then go sell it or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says our meat stinks too much to buy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Then throw it away, for all I care.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.59,0:13:50.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu, why's Dad doing this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.59,0:13:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad likes the hunt itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.11,0:13:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever disobey him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.13,0:14:01.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He may turn around one day and hunt us too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.53,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,If you ever think we're in danger, we'll run away like Mom did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.37,0:14:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have the ability too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.31,0:14:12.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll keep you safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.85,0:14:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,'Kay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.24,0:14:21.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Not long after that, Dad started to change.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.85,0:14:24.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.92,0:14:25.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:27.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Something weird's happening to Dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.54,0:14:32.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It's like he's turning invisible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.49,0:14:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad's shadow is gone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.08,0:14:50.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, that same day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.66,0:14:53.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad, we brought you breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.31,0:14:56.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Dad?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.90,0:15:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,He just disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.99,0:15:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Supposedly, when a very powerful fuki host passes on,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:16.73,Default,,0,0,0,,his descendants' abilities become enhanced, as if unleashed from a bind.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.99,0:15:23.19,Default,,0,0,0,,In afflicted hosts, fuki spreads until it gains total control over the body.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words, the host passes over to the mushi's world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.27,0:15:31.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Your dad isn't dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.95,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,But he lost his physical form... as well as his soul.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,He's probably still wandering in these mountains somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.55,0:15:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So if we don't do something soon, Tatsu's going to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can smell that sweet scent again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.51,0:15:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, hi. You made it back, huh, Ginko?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.07,0:15:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.06,0:16:00.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I brought the kouki for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.11,0:16:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got to drink it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.47,0:16:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,You can give Usuke his first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.67,0:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll drink mine when I feel like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.01,0:16:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Must be nice, feeling like you rule over the whole mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.27,0:16:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's time to open your eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.51,0:16:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You're being manipulated by a mushi that doesn't even have conscious thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.49,0:16:27.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut the hell up.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.13,0:16:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You really don't know your place, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.25,0:16:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Just give Usuke his, and then leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.15,0:16:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I never want us to feel that way again...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.73,0:16:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the way we did when {\i1}he{\i0} was alive...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.35,0:16:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,like we could be hunted down any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.41,0:16:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's enough, Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.75,0:16:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We're all right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.67,0:16:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't have to be afraid anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.99,0:16:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I even figured out a way so we can avoid being attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.75,0:17:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,So please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.95,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.36,0:17:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Where did he go?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.52,0:17:25.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.87,0:17:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I have to go back...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.67,0:17:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to the person I used to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.23,0:17:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Usuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.97,0:17:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.21,0:17:54.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you shoot at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.97,0:17:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I think it was a bear,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.74,0:17:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,but whatever it was fell down the cliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.07,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is fuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.10,0:18:14.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Damn it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.11,0:18:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can't move my arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.97,0:18:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}If I don't figure something out soon, the wild beasts will eat me alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.07,0:18:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Maybe I'll be safe here until morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.19,0:19:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The night has never felt this long.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.66,0:19:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}And the darkness has never been... this terrifying.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.23,0:19:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:33.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.37,0:19:36.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm over here, Usuke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.19,0:19:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu—
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.39,0:19:51.12,Default,,0,0,0,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.12,0:19:52.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait! Don't come out yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.35,0:19:54.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.39,0:20:24.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did the birds... attack my arm like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.27,0:20:30.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Most animals—birds in particular—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.17,0:20:32.41,Default,,0,0,0,,fear marks that resemble eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.59,0:20:35.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Although they were all drawn to that sweet scent,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.49,0:20:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,they never attacked your hand, because of that mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.19,0:20:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,But once the "eye" became covered in your fuki-scented blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.49,0:20:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the birds only saw your arm as irresistible food.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.83,0:20:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Food for the birds, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.56,0:20:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Tatsu, your fever's gone down a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.97,0:21:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You look like you've gotten a lot better too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.64,0:21:03.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.42,0:21:05.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't coughed up any blood at all lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.32,0:21:07.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that kouki thing really worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I can learn how to hunt too.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.68,0:21:14.08,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to get better too so we can go hunting together, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.95,0:21:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.51,0:21:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.23,0:21:39.38,Default,,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.38,0:21:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't scare me like that.{lol Ginko}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.75,0:21:48.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}In the dark, even the bravest \Nbecome afraid of unseen phantoms.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.67,0:21:55.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cavorting under the shroud of darkness... are countless misshapen entities.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.23,0:22:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}But if ever there were a king of the creatures of the night...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}surely, it would look just like that.
